  <li>
    <p>She had always counted on that hatred, she had felt it in the air when the phantom was near, and the mere sight of him had upset and frightened her so that she never found a natural way to <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="behave with him"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(面对他)</code></b>.</p>
